assert lpluck('dst', idb.analysis.get_crefs_from(kernel32_idb, 1754273429)
    ) == []
assert lpluck('dst', idb.analysis.get_crefs_from(kernel32_idb, 1754273438)
    ) == [1754292566]
assert lpluck('src', idb.analysis.get_crefs_to(kernel32_idb, 1754273438)) == []
assert lpluck('src', idb.analysis.get_crefs_to(kernel32_idb, 1754292566)) == [
    1754273438]
security_cookie = 1755165552
assert lpluck('dst', idb.analysis.get_drefs_from(kernel32_idb, 1754273472)
    ) == [security_cookie]
assert lpluck('src', idb.analysis.get_drefs_to(kernel32_idb, 1754273472)) == []
assert 1754273472 in pluck('src', idb.analysis.get_drefs_to(kernel32_idb,
    security_cookie))
assert lpluck('dst', idb.analysis.get_drefs_from(kernel32_idb, security_cookie)
    ) == []
kern32_test()
